Sketch a circle.



```js
circle(center: [number], radius: number, tag?: String, sketch_surface_or_group: SketchSurfaceOrGroup) -> SketchGroup
```

### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn("-XZ")
  |> circle([0, 0], 10, %)

const example = extrude(5, exampleSketch)
```
